{"tid":1838552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"SARS冇藥醫WARS冇都藥醫，再唔封城全港都冇藥醫","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T05:42:52.000Z","uid":233692,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d63c1ce988cefd98a86671e417d978fbe22fc10","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"沙士冇藥醫 到2020都冇藥醫<br />\n服用高劑量類固醇會導致骨枯<br />\n而後期發現如果係病發初期用高劑量類固醇，會令病情惡化<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重申沙士無藥醫</span><br />\n你只可以打疫苗增強免疫力對抗，一係就等死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">SARS疫苗研發左10年都研發唔到<br />\n係2013年已經放棄左研發啦</span><br />\n<br />\n要研發疫苗就要揾到病源嘅基因排序普圖，當初中大化學病理學系系主任盧煜明率領團隊研究沙士病毒基因圖譜，用了十三天把沙士基因成功排序，用圖譜便知病毒演變及傳染方式等。<br />\n<br />\n佢咁快排序到因為係蝙蝠揾到病源乍。依加佢成個武漢華南超市消滅證據，病源由排先追蹤到，都唔知係邊隻動物來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">WARS重係到變緊種，研究到疫苗已經太遲了。</span><br />\n<br />\n潘續說，若沙士重臨，現存藥苗應有冠狀病毒的基因綫譜，<span style=\"color: red;\">「在此基礎下改良，最快三至六個月可投入生產，但恐怕已太遲。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙士研究煞停 十年無解藥 經費少資源缺 進展零聲氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/reporterwilliam.wordpress.com/2013/03/22/sars10years/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Freporterwilliam.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F03%2F22%2Fsars10years%2Famp%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=acfa944a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/reporterwilliam.wordpress.com/2013/03/22/sars10years/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工封城唯一出路</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15379a7299a25f141aef204a0cdf8fbbc96960ec","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtF45O8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtF45O8.jpg&h=3be5e757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等唔到初三了"},{"pid":"a4cb145fce8827dee0a7bccb7739cde3d10113b0","tid":1838552,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"14b23ce3fbce7f3a01e9e120a2b4b90597d4d2eb","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZV45Po.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZV45Po.jpg&h=9f9b4249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要命定要錢<br />\n錢都比晒popo"},{"pid":"bfa2adf7eb0702d89f23bc1f78f5cc1010291c42","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qv2rzH3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQv2rzH3.jpg&h=24949e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾日後香港充滿呢啲廢人"},{"pid":"757bafdf704fe7c459ac772da50a6950b4ad8ee3","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mu2yY99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMu2yY99.png&h=59d7a34b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疫苗都冇支呀<br />\n<br />\n啲設備唔夠隔離