苗係要提早打,需要一段時間你既身體去做免疫記憶先有用"},{"pid":"e9707a5adcd0e2128f370407e9570bbba1a4154e","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9f40a1cde1edaac30d469050afb3f0e473098f","tid":1838552,"uid":18803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"好多病毒不嬲都冇咩藥醫 唔係淨係sars同今次大陸病毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎致命率高，所以唔封城等死<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51202544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-51202544&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=8c3b94bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51202544</a><br />\n//中國新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎確診病例444例，累積死亡個案17例。//<br />\n佢琴且公佈嘅數字乍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f151e7b61270d3881ebb4be5ebcba70a5674c1","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b8d35eb2fb5a68a20ecdb2e33cf7074bd2f8c82","tid":1838552,"uid":336337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d63c1ce988cefd98a86671e417d978fbe22fc10","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"沙士冇藥醫 到2020都冇藥醫<br />\n服用高劑量類固醇會導致骨枯<br />\n而後期發現如果係病發初期用高劑量類固醇，會令病情惡化<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重申沙士無藥醫</span><br />\n你只可以打疫苗增強免疫力對抗，一係就等死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">SARS疫苗研發左10年都研發唔到<br />\n係2013年已經放棄左研發啦</span><br />\n<br />\n要研發疫苗就要揾到病源嘅基因排序普圖，當初中大化學病理學系系主任盧煜明率領團隊研究沙士病毒基因圖譜，用了十三天把沙士基因成功排序，用圖譜便知病毒演變及傳染方式等。<br />\n<br />\n佢咁快排序到因為係蝙蝠揾到病源乍。依加佢成個武漢華南超市消滅證據，病源由排先追蹤到，都唔知係邊隻動物來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">WARS重係到變緊種，研究到疫苗已經太遲了。</span><br />\n<br />\n潘續說，若沙士重臨，現存藥苗應有冠狀病毒的基因綫譜，<span style=\"color: red;\">「在此基礎下改良，最快三至六個月可投入生產，但恐怕已太遲。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙士研究煞停 十年無解藥 經費少資源缺 進展零聲氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/reporterwilliam.wordpress.com/2013/03/22/sars10years/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Freporterwilliam.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F03%2F22%2Fsars10years%2Famp%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=acfa944a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/reporterwilliam.wordpress.com/2013/03/22/sars10years/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工封城唯一出路</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"&quot;你只可以打疫苗增強免疫力對抗，一係就等死&quot;<br />\n疫苗係幫你身體對特定一種病源體有抵制力,做免疫記憶<br />\n你打A疫苗係抵抗唔到B病源體,所以大家唔好亂打(雖然正常唔會有問題),打左第2隻,係唔會令你對WARS既免疫力增加<br />\n另外,疫苗係要提早打,需要一段時間你既身體去做免疫記憶先有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"研發得來又要半年<br />\n打完都死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56fa63bf03afa2d7c97b9469830255f7954a734","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9707a5adcd0e2128f370407e9570bbba1a4154e","tid":1838552,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9f40a1cde1edaac30d469050afb3f0e473098f","tid":1838552,"uid":18803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"好多病毒不嬲都冇咩藥醫 唔係淨係sars同今次大陸病毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎致命率高，所以唔封城等死<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/ch